<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="hw20Dec1934"><font color="red">20 December 1934</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): An hour after our telephone conversation on Tuesday evening (18 December 1934) I received &hellip; a long letter from Mr Joyce enclosing a batch of MS of the piece he is working on. He told me that, five weeks before, he decided to go back to Paris, set up the flat and return to Zurich for Christmas &hellip; scene &hellip; he stayed on. </div>
